yazawa_quest_a301.title: Special Delivery: Straight Outta Paper
yazawa_quest_a301.detail: I was on the toilet because of my stomach, and well, I noticed there's no toilet paper... Please bring me one pack of Pocket Tissues to the restrooms at Hamakita Park!

yazawa_quest_a302.title: Special Delivery: Station Constipation
yazawa_quest_a302.detail: I'm in a restroom with, um, no toilet paper again... Please bring me two packs of Pocket Tissues to the restrooms in front of Jinnai Station!

yazawa_quest_a303.title: Special Delivery: Big Rumble in Little China
yazawa_quest_a303.detail: I'm in a restroom with, um, no toilet paper once again... Please bring me three packs of Pocket Tissues to the restrooms in Chinatown!

yazawa_quest_a304.title: Special Delivery: Closed for Construction
yazawa_quest_a304.detail: I couldn't keep the floodgates closed, so I ran into a portable toilet at some construction site and, well, no toilet paper... Please bring me five packs of Pocket Tissues at Tsurukame Alley!

yazawa_quest_a305.title: Special Delivery: Shit Outta Luck
yazawa_quest_a305.detail: How could a restaurant be out of toilet paper...? Please bring me ten packs of Pocket Tissues to the restrooms in Wette Kitchen!

yazawa_quest_a306.title: Missing: Willful Son
yazawa_quest_a306.detail: My son Daisuke went missing... I'm sure he ran off to the capsule machines again, but I'm worried all the same. Would you please contact me the moment you find him?

yazawa_quest_a307.title: Missing: Peeved Girlfriend
yazawa_quest_a307.detail: TLDR: Me and my girlfriend had an argument, I said something dumb, she stormed out of the apartment. What I did was buy her favorite donuts instead of going to look for herthat's what I'm hiring you for. Please, bring Tomoko back home!

yazawa_quest_a308.title: Missing: Homeless Wreck
yazawa_quest_a308.detail: Ever since my husband lost his business, he's refused to come back home. Instead, he's been living on the streets, as if he's too ashamed to face me... Anyway, I heard from a friend there's a specific place in Yokohama where lots of homeless people gather, and that's where he is. His name is Michiake, so please talk some sense into him!

yazawa_quest_a309.title: Missing: Fellow Gaijin
yazawa_quest_a309.detail: I am Mike. My travel buddy Dave and I got separated. Please find him and let me know. When Dave gets tired, he goes to a bench.

yazawa_quest_a310.title: Missing: Whipped Husband
yazawa_quest_a310.detail: I swear, this husband of mine... All he does is find excuses to get out of the house. Knowing him, he's probably off drinking at a bar. I shouldn't have to be the one dragging him back, so you go do it instead. His name is Takaaki, but he also responds to "buffoon," "piglet," and "Mr. Disappointment."

yazawa_quest_a311.title: Please Find My Cat 1
yazawa_quest_a311.detail: My cats have gone off somewhere while I was busy saving the city as a hero... Would you please find my nine cats in Yokohama!? Please report directly back to me when you've found them!

yazawa_quest_a312.title: Please Find My Cat 2
yazawa_quest_a312.detail: Unlike my other ones, it may be difficult to find my Robson-chan. But I believe in you, Kasuga-san! Please find Robson-chan, my first cat love!

yazawa_quest_a316.title: Kappture the Kappa
yazawa_quest_a316.detail: There are kappa here... in Yokohama! But the only suggestion of their existence is in symbols. Finding these alone in such a large city is a lot of work... I heard that there are ten of them so I would like you to photograph these for me!

yazawa_quest_a801.title: SOS: Carriage Highway
yazawa_quest_a801.detail: Please get these punks off my case! I'm around Carriage Highway, so get here as soon as possible!

yazawa_quest_a802.title: SOS: Hakuryo Building
yazawa_quest_a802.detail: Some maniacs are running amok, and now they've set their sights on me! I'm in front of the Hakuryo Building on Carriage Highway! Get rid of them at all costs!

yazawa_quest_a803.title: SOS: West Bayside St.
yazawa_quest_a803.detail: It's been a while since I've left the house, and as soon as I started enjoying myself, I realized I was being followed! If you have any kindness in your heart, you'll save me! I'm in the West Bayside Street area!

yazawa_quest_a811.title: SOS: Hamakita Park Seaside
yazawa_quest_a811.detail: These douchebags are harassing me and my date! Jealous much? Anyway, we're at Hamakita Park, so get over here and do your job!

yazawa_quest_a812.title: SOS: Hamakita Park Dragon Kart Registry
yazawa_quest_a812.detail: For some odd reason, my birdwatching regimen attracted the attention of some really foul people. I'm near the Dragon Kart registration in Hamakita Park. Care to shoo them away?

yazawa_quest_a813.title: SOS: Hamakita Park Entrance
yazawa_quest_a813.detail: Some creep wandered up to us and my boyfriend just took off running! What a bastard! Anyway, I'm near the Hamakita Park entrance, so hurry up and beat this guy to a pulp!

yazawa_quest_a821.title: SOS: Chinatown Parking Structure
yazawa_quest_a821.detail: So I was going souvenir shopping when all of a sudden I got mugged, and the police are nowhere to be found! Way to create a safe shopping atmosphere! This happened near the parking structure.

yazawa_quest_a822.title: SOS: Chinatown Park
yazawa_quest_a822.detail: I was doing some location scouting, and next thing I know, I'm being pulled aside by some thugs. This is my first assignment to get approved, so I can't afford to screw things up! I'm at the park in Chinatown and would greatly appreciate some help!

yazawa_quest_a823.title: SOS: Chinatown Public Restrooms
yazawa_quest_a823.detail: So here I am on a food tour, happily munching away, when some weirdo came up and started heckling me for food. I'm in front of the public restrooms and could use some weirdo removal ASAP!

yazawa_quest_a831.title: SOS: Yokohama Blvd.
yazawa_quest_a831.detail: All I wanted to do was take a walk, and now these people are threatening me! Why does this always happen!? I may be on Yokohama Boulevard, but I'm in dire straits!

yazawa_quest_a832.title: SOS: Isobe Alley
yazawa_quest_a832.detail: I'm trying to enjoy my solo Korean food tour, but this creep won't leave me alone! What part of solo does he not understand? Anyway, I'm over by Isobe Alley, so can someone come get rid of this guy?

yazawa_quest_a833.title: SOS: Fukutokucho
yazawa_quest_a833.detail: Some punks are demanding a fee from everyone walking by. I'd say I chose the wrong day to go out for kimchi, but I refuse to take this lying down! I'm in Fukutokucho, so hurry and give me some backup!

yazawa_quest_a841.title: SOS: Bar District Bike Racks
yazawa_quest_a841.detail: I bumped into this one person on my way back from the bar and now he won't leave me alone... I know I started this, but I'm not paying up that much! I'm at the bike racks in the Bar District! Please intervene!

yazawa_quest_a842.title: SOS: Near Survive Bar
yazawa_quest_a842.detail: I took a quick glance at some stranger and now he's practically threatening to kill me! I told him it was a misunderstanding, but all he does is shout over me. I'm over by Survive... Fitting name for a bar, because I really hope I make it out alive!

yazawa_quest_a843.title: SOS: Bar District Parking Lot
yazawa_quest_a843.detail: So I tried this new bar, but now they want to rip me off! You'll see me at the parking lot in the Bar District, so can you come help sort this out?

yazawa_quest_a851.title: SOS: S Sakura River St.
yazawa_quest_a851.detail: I've been framed as a thief and now I'm being asked to hand over my belongings. Please believe me when I say I haven't stolen a thing! This is happening near the parking structure... I could really use a hero right now!

yazawa_quest_a852.title: SOS: Misaki St.
yazawa_quest_a852.detail: This is going to sound awkward, but I'm being accused of lechery. Like, being a pervert. I'm at Misaki Street, so can you come help me talk this guy down? It's pretty obvious he's just trying to get some hush money out of me.

yazawa_quest_a853.title: SOS: Tsurukame Alley
yazawa_quest_a853.detail: Some scary guy bumped into me, yet he's the one claiming he got hurt. Wants me to pay for damages, too. I'm at a construction site in Tsurukame Alley. Can you help me get rid of this faker?

yazawa_quest_a861.title: SOS: Central St.
yazawa_quest_a861.detail: This recruiter's being super inappropriate. I keep telling him off, but he isn't taking no for an answer, so maybe you could deliver the message with a little more... force? I'm over here on Central Street.

yazawa_quest_a862.title: SOS: Romance St.
yazawa_quest_a862.detail: Dammit all! I was all set to have Ai-chan knead my dangle dough, but now this thug wants to shake me down instead! Can't a man get massaged in peace!? Urrrrgh! Just hurry down to Romance Street, before I lose my leavening!

yazawa_quest_a863.title: SOS: Central St. Parking Lot
yazawa_quest_a863.detail: Some group claiming to be backed by the Seiryu Clan won't stop trying to recruit me. I'm not even sure if it's legit... Can you take care of these guys in the Parking Lot on Central Street?

yazawa_quest_a871.title: SOS: E Tsurukame Highway
yazawa_quest_a871.detail: I was doing some investigative journalism on Ijincho, but then some really aggressive people started barking orders at me! I still don't understand what they want! I'm on East Tsurukame Highway! Please hurry!

yazawa_quest_a872.title: SOS: Hyakkei Alley
yazawa_quest_a872.detail: So these guys are on the street demanding money or blood from anyone walking by. Yeah... I don't get it either. I'm in a small alley off of Hyakkei Street if you think you can help.

yazawa_quest_a873.title: SOS: Hyakkei St.
yazawa_quest_a873.detail: My beloved and I were to meet not far from here, but some evildoers must have caught wind of it; they now endeavor to seize my coinpurse and all the wherewithal therein! I beg you, make haste to Hyakkei Street before the stars cross my love any further!
